Summary: Based on the provided bullet points, it seems that the reviews for the restaurant Betty Jeanz Sole Food have some negative sentiment regarding the food quality and service. Several customers mentioned that the food quality was mediocre and did not meet their expectations. In addition, there were also complaints about the long wait times for the food, with some customers mentioning that they had to wait almost 2 hours to be served. This is definitely a major issue that can impact the overall dining experience and lead to frustration and disappointment among customers. Overall, it seems that the restaurant needs to work on improving the quality of their food and the speed of their service to better meet the expectations of their customers. By addressing these issues, they can potentially improve their reputation and attract more positive reviews in the future.
